<p>3DMODEL-CHECKER automatically enables quantitative adjudication on data measurement and specification confirmation. 3DMODEL-CHECKER makes it easier to check data of 3D die/mold drawings.<br><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">How 3DMODEL-CHECKER Automatically Checks Drawings</h2><p>3DMODEL-CHECKER facilitates drawings checks through quantitatively adjudicating on data measurement and specifications confirmation.<br>First, prepare correct data for checking drawings in advance.<br>The System automatically aligns the data for checking drawings with the corresponding data of 3D die/mold designs, and adjudicates on acceptability.<br>Also, 3DMODEL-CHECKER automatically checks drawings in coordination with the Excel Cooperation functions.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/349F3B6D-BF38-80B6-BB3D-FFDF3EA48952.jpeg" alt="How 3DMODEL-CHECKER Automatically Checks Drawings" width="700" height="418" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">3D Model-Checker Capable of Confirming the Items Below</h2><p>Verify sizes of parts and part constituents</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/288611B7-9936-A684-7472-972DD58B8AA5.jpeg" alt="3D Model-Checker Capable of Confirming the Items Below 1" width="700" height="414" class="fr-fic fr-dii"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/C5EC8EAA-29B5-1FFD-4C37-AC4AA7A192AF.jpeg" alt="3D Model-Checker Capable of Confirming the Items Below 2" width="700" height="442" class="fr-fic fr-dii"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/AB347B2B-7B8F-34F2-8DE0-ECD57AA523A1.jpeg" alt="3D Model-Checker Capable of Confirming the Items Below 3" width="700" height="436" class="fr-fic fr-dii">(*) Please note that 3D Model-Checker verification capabilities are not enabled depending upon how subject design data was created.</p><p align="center"><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Mechanism</h2><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/E68B34FC-1661-943A-A0D1-B095529ED2FF.jpeg" alt="Mechanism" width="700" height="427" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Use Examples (U-groove)</h2><h3>Preliminary Preparations about Drawing Check Data (Example: U-groove)</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/5076D282-206F-3AC7-770A-07A739C17ACC.jpeg" alt="Preliminary Preparations about Drawing Check Data (Example: U-groove)" width="700" height="410" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Output Example (U-groove)</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/0C1901DA-4C92-0F1B-E84D-95026C5B12C7.jpeg" alt="Output Example (U-groove)" width="700" height="438" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>All computation results including coordinate values can be output to Excel spreadsheets.<br>CADmeister 2024 supports the Excel Macro capabilities. This enables CADmeister 2024 to automatically check a position of U groove (in light of T Slot, an operation area of &quot;Auto Clamper&quot; , etc.)<br><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Use Examples (Side Pins)</h2><h3>Preliminary Preparations about Drawing Check Data (Example: Side Pins)</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/0670C49A-86D2-BA8D-A52C-A8A0361C79AD.jpeg" alt="Preliminary Preparations about Drawing Check Data (Example: Side Pins)" width="700" height="415" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Output (Example: Side Pins ①）</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/54312822-3DCC-3D33-F7AB-32A2DB24427D.jpeg" alt="Output (Example:  Side Pins ①）" width="700" height="398" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h4><br></h4><h3>Output (Example: Side Pins ②）</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/4ECA0CBA-B478-0934-4371-988D681F9CD8.jpeg" alt="Output (Example:  Side Pins ②）" width="700" height="493" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Output (Example: Side Pins ③）</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/DAE0DBBB-8FD4-230F-7497-B4EA982FA211.jpeg" alt="Output (Example:  Side Pins ③）" width="700" height="480" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Use Examples (Spring)</h2><h3>Preliminary Preparations about Drawing Check Data (Example: Springs)</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/4424F847-71A3-783A-F73B-E840855EEC1B.jpeg" alt="Preliminary Preparations about Drawing Check Data (Example: Springs)" width="450" height="400" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h3>Output Example (Springs)</h3><hr><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/5E49F662-9B9D-5E88-65BE-EDFB1F899A9C.jpeg" alt="Output Example (Springs)" width="700" height="462" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Confirm Steel Materials&#39; Sizes</h2><p>The System automatically measures 3D steel materials in three-dimensions (the x-axis, the y-axis, and the z-axis), and outputs measurement results.<br>Also, the System automatically compares the results with sizes of ordered parts described in Parts Lists, and outputs results of adjudication on acceptability.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/C1F7400B-A555-DA32-E877-F7057D231A05.jpeg" alt="Confirm Steel Materials’ Sizes" width="700" height="431" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">List of Tap Holes and Reamer Holes</h2><p>The System automatically checks diameters, depths, and RGB colors of holes that are tapped/reamed in 3D data for the purposes of installation and positioning, and lists results.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/329F72E0-BE09-81E9-1484-4999F1083DF2.jpeg" alt="List of Tap Holes and Reamer Holes" width="700" height="314" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3>&nbsp;Inquiries</h3><p>If you have any inquiries about our product or would like to request a visit to your place for explanation or demonstration, please use the inquiry form.<br>&nbsp;</p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>